    <ResearchProjectDef>
        <defName>PM_PurifierProjectFinal</defName>
        <label>Eclipse and Apocalypse</label>
        <description>"We are the Purifiers.  We were the spear of the Empire, the honourable Templar.  To better defend the Empire, we joined the Purifier Project, prepared to offer our eternal loyalty and service with honour.  Yet the High Conclave betrayed us—betrayed everyone.  We fought with honour, but they treated us as nothing more than machines.  So be it—let war come!  Let the universe boil, let the stars fall!  We gave them a chance, and they called it weakness.  Mercy is no more.  Traitors, the time has come to pay the price.  TIME IS TOO LATE, Organics." \n\n  —— Purifier Executor Clolarion</description>
        <tab>ProtossTech</tab>
